<div class="container-fluid mt-5">
    <div class="col-12 card mt-3">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-9 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                <h4 class="card-header  text-center bg-info text-white" style="font-size:22px;">
                    BRANCH OFFICE
                </h4>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                            <img src="~/Content/images/BRANCH.png" class="img-fluid img-thumbnail" style="max-height:320px;min-height:300px;" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                            <div class="text-justify" style="font-size:18px;">
                                Branch office means a office which is located somewhere other than main office location. A branch office is simply another location, and is still involved in the business activities of the organization.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                                @*<div class="text-justify" style="font-size:18px;">
                                    It's a simply firm which is
                                    enabling doing business in India with Less Compliance and Less Costing. a Sole Proprietorship
                                </div>*@
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 float-right">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="mb-2">
                        <form class="form" action="/Home/Enquiry" method="post">
                            <div class="card">
                                <div class="card-header bg-info">
                                    <div class="text-center" style="font-size:20px; color:aliceblue;">REQUEST A CALL BACK</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <div class="form-group">
                                        <label for="name"><b></b></label>
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control" style="font-size:15px;" id="txtname" name="txtname" placeholder="Your Name" required>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="form-group">
                                        <label for="email"><B></B></label>
                                        <input type="email" class="form-control" style="font-size:15px;" id="txtemail" name="txtemail" placeholder="Email Address" required>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="form-group">
                                        <label for="num"><B></B></label>
                                        <div class="input-group">
                                            <span class="input-group-addon bg-light p-1">+91 </span>
                                            <input type="tel" class="form-control " style="font-size:15px;" id="txtnumber" name="txtnumber" placeholder="Please Enter Number" required>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg float-right" style="font-size:18px;">Get Start</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
   
        <div class="bg-light card">
            <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
                <h2 class="text-left" style="font-size:21px;">Process</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <ol style="font-size:18px;">
                    <li>Attestation or Legalisation of Documents</li>
                    <li>Filing of Application with RBI through AD Bank</li>
                    <li>Verification of KYC from Banker of Parent Company</li>
                    <li>Approval of RBI for Liasion Office Registration in India</li>
                    <li>Registration of Liasion office of Foreign Company with the ROC</li>
                    <li>PAN Card, Tax Deduction Number & Bank A/c Opening</li>
                    <li class="text-justify">
                        Other Registration and Licenses For example registration under shops and establishment act, Goods
                        and Services Tax (GST), Professional Tax Act, Provident Funds Act, Employee State Insurance Act
                        (ESIC), etc.
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-light card">
            <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
                <h2 class="text-left" style="font-size:21px;">General Criteria – Branch Office</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="text-justify" style="font-size:18px;">
                    A body corporate incorporated outside India (including a firm or other association of individuals), desirous of opening a Branch Office (BO) in India have to obtain permission from the Reserve Bank under provisions of FEMA 1999.
                    -	Application in the prescribed Form FNC shall be filed (WMC to be provide post receipt of information as per this checklist)

                </p>
